   3.63320571676738*^9},ExpressionUUID->"beecd915-fcb5-4fd6-b1bd-\
2deaf9bddf91"],

Cell[TextData[StyleBox["As these are discrete points, we need to interpolate \
to obtain an input function for our model:",
 FontSize->18]], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.602970163819399*^9, 
  3.602970188682268*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"24bfa59d-4e6e-4c0f-b271-\
eb688ae97567"],

